data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
1. Click "Download SteamCMD" (If you haven't) 2. Locate your SteamCMD (If it isn't located) 3. Choose your server 4. Type quit, if the download was successful 5. Create server files(.bat and.cfg)(Optional for some games) 6. Edit your server's settings (Optional)(Change server name, password, map, gamemode) 7. Start the server and have fun!
Note: This Tool will ONLY install the Server, it can´t forward any ports for you!
